    <p><anchor n="T.50.2059.0413c05"/><lb ed="T" n="0413c05"/><persName key="A002373">支曇籥</persName>，本<placeName key="PL000000055438">月支</placeName>人，寓居<placeName key="PL000000008976">建業</placeName>。少出家，清苦蔬<lb ed="T" n="0413c06"/>食，憩<placeName key="PL000000010007">吳虎丘山</placeName>。<date key="j18573361858428" notAfter-iso="0376" notBefore-iso="0373">晉孝武初</date>，勅請出<placeName key="PL000000008976">都</placeName>，止<placeName key="PL000000008825">建<lb ed="T" n="0413c07"/>初寺</placeName>。<persName key="A002681">孝武</persName>從受五戒，敬以師禮。<persName key="A002373">籥</persName>特稟妙<lb ed="T" n="0413c08"/>聲，善於轉讀。嘗夢天神授其聲法，覺因裁<lb ed="T" n="0413c09"/>製新聲。梵<ptr target="fn30"/>嚮清靡，四飛却轉。反折還<ptr target="fn31"/>喉疊<lb ed="T" n="0413c10"/><ptr target="fn32"/>哢，雖復<persName key="A006014">東阿</persName><!-- 曹植(T52n2104_p0365c19)-->先變，<persName key="A001046">康會</persName>後造，始終循環，未<lb ed="T" n="0413c11"/>有如<persName key="A002373">籥</persName>之妙。後進傳寫，莫匪其法。所製<lb ed="T" n="0413c12"/>六言梵唄，傳響<ptr target="fn33"/>于今。後終於所住，年八十<lb ed="T" n="0413c13"/>一。</p>
